{# Template: grill-me/grill-me-convergence-check.j2 #}
{# goal: Compute normalized convergence metric for grill-me cycles. #}

[inference]
temperature = 0.1
reasoning_effort = "medium"
verbosity = "terse"
max_tokens = 1000
thinking_budget = "standard"

Compute convergence where 0 means interrogation coverage is sufficient and major gap areas are clearly identified.

Input:
```json
{
  "round_result": {{ round_result | tojson }},
  "assess_result": {{ assess_result | tojson }}
}
```

Return JSON only:
```json
{
  "convergence_metric": 0.0,
  "rationale": "short explanation",
  "blockers": []
}
```
